The mayor of Minami Soma, a small city next to the crippled Fukushima nuclear
power plant, asked for help through a [video [en, ja] posted on
Youtube](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=70ZHQ--cK40). The mayor launched an
appeal to the world saying the people are isolated, there is a lack of
supplies and the government is not delivering necessity goods to the citizens
who were ordered to evacuate.

